  <bioghist id="aspace_bbdbfeec952ab661da9818381d8814a5">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The New York State Veterinary Medical Society Auxiliary is a women's organization affiliated with the New York State Veterinary Medical Society.</p>  </bioghist>
  <relatedmaterial id="aspace_12d9a6314e75040800d2ccba01122a04">
    <head>RELATED MATERIAL</head>
